SELECT NVL(TRIM(EN.M_LABEL), ' ') AS M_ENTITY, ACG.M_EN_AMT AS M_EN_AMT, ACG.M_EN_COMMENT AS M_EN_COMMENT, NVL(AD.M_LABEL, ' ') AS M_EN_DEBIT  , NVL(AC.M_LABEL, ' ') AS M_EN_CREDIT, P1.M_CURRENCY AS M_EN_CUR, P2.M_CURRENCY AS M_X_CUR, ACG.M_EN_DATE AS M_EN_DATE, ACG. M_VAL_DATE AS M_VAL_DATE, ACG.M_EN_TYPE AS M_EN_TYPE, ACG.M_STP_STATUS AS M_STP_STATUS, ACG.M_NB AS M_NB, ACG.M_NB_PREV AS M_NB_PREV, ACG.M_NB_REVERSE AS M_NB_REVERSE, ACG.M_NB_OFFSET AS M_NB_OFFSET, ACG.M_EN_OFFSET AS M_EN_OFFSET, ACG.M_NB_RULE AS M_NB_RULE, ACG.M_NB_TRN AS M_NB_TRN, ACG.M_NB_TRN_QTY AS M_NB_TRN_QTY, NVL(I.M_FAMILY, ' ') AS M_TRN_FMLY, NVL(I.M_GROUP, ' ')  AS M_TRN_GRP , NVL(I.M_TYPE, ' ')   AS M_TRN_TYPE, ACG.M_TYPE_NB AS M_TYPE_NB, ACG.M_EN_NETTED AS M_EN_NETTED, ACG.M_NB_MOP AS M_NB_MOP, ACG.M_NB_BS AS M_NB_BS, ACG.M_PAY_DAT AS M_PAY_DAT, ACG.M_RES_FLG AS M_RES_FLG, ACG.M_SYS_DATE AS M_SYS_DATE, ACG.M_SIGN AS M_SIGN, ACG.M_HDG_TYPE AS M_HDG_TYPE, ACG.M_EVT_INTID AS M_EVT_INTID, ACC.M_LABEL AS M_ACC_SEC, HDRUDF.M_ACU_DBU AS M_ACU_DBU, HDRUDF.M_BRW_NOMU1 AS M_BRW_NOMU1, HDRUDF.M_BRW_NOMU2 AS M_BRW_NOMU2, TO_DATE(@REPORTING_DATE:D,'YYYYMMDD') AS M_H_REP_DATE FROM ACG_ENTRY_DBF ACG LEFT OUTER JOIN TRN_ENTD_DBF EN      ON ACG.M_ENTITY = EN.M_REF LEFT OUTER JOIN TRN_PLIN_DBF P1      ON ACG.M_INSTRUMENT = P1.M_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN TRN_PLIN_DBF P2      ON ACG.M_X_INSTRUMENT = P2.M_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN TRN_ACA1_DBF AC      ON ACG.M_EN_CREDIT = AC.M_REFERENCE LEFT OUTER JOIN TRN_ACA1_DBF AD      ON ACG.M_EN_DEBIT = AD.M_REFERENCE LEFT OUTER JOIN INSTTYPE_DBF I      ON ACG.M_TRN_FGT = I.M_GLOBREF LEFT OUTER JOIN TRN_ACSC_DBF ACC      ON ACG.M_ACC_SEC = ACC.M_REFERENCE LEFT OUTER JOIN           (SELECT              HDR.M_NB AS M_NB,            HDR.M_BRW_NOMU1 AS M_BRW_NOMU1,            HDR.M_BRW_NOMU2 AS M_BRW_NOMU2,             DC.M_ACU_DBU AS M_ACU_DBU          FROM TABLE#DATA#DEALCURR_DBF DC, TRN_EXT_DBF EXT, TRN_HDR_DBF HDR          WHERE (HDR.M_BENTITY='SG' OR HDR.M_SENTITY='SG') ANDDC.M_NB = EXT.M_UDF_REF          AND EXT.M_TRADE_REF = HDR.M_NB                   UNION          SELECT             HDR.M_NB AS M_NB,            HDR.M_BRW_NOMU1 AS M_BRW_NOMU1,            HDR.M_BRW_NOMU2 AS M_BRW_NOMU2,             DI.M_ACU_DBU AS M_ACU_DBU          FROM TABLE#DATA#DEALIRD_DBF DI, TRN_EXT_DBF EXT, TRN_HDR_DBF HDR          WHERE (HDR.M_BENTITY='SG' OR HDR.M_SENTITY='SG') AND          DI.M_NB = EXT.M_UDF_REF          AND EXT.M_TRADE_REF = HDR.M_NB          UNION          SELECT             HDR.M_NB AS M_NB,            HDR.M_BRW_NOMU1 AS M_BRW_NOMU1,            HDR.M_BRW_NOMU2 AS M_BRW_NOMU2,             DS.M_ACU_DBU AS M_ACU_DBU           FROM TABLE#DATA#DEALSCF_DBF DS, TRN_EXT_DBF EXT, TRN_HDR_DBF HDR          WHERE (HDR.M_BENTITY='SG' OR HDR.M_SENTITY='SG') AND          DS.M_NB = EXT.M_UDF_REF          AND EXT.M_TRADE_REF = HDR.M_NB          ) HDRUDF   ON ACG.M_NB_TRN = HDRUDF.M_NB WHERE M_EN_DATE=@REPORTING_DATE:D

SELECT     NVL(TRIM(EN.M_LABEL), ' ') AS M_ENTITY,    NVL(A.M_LABEL, ' ') AS M_EN_ACCOUNT,  ACJS.M_EN_AMTC AS M_EN_AMTC,  ACJS.M_EN_AMTD AS M_EN_AMTD,  ACJS.M_EN_AMTN AS M_EN_AMTN,  ACJS.M_EN_DATE AS M_EN_DATE,  ACJS.M_INSTRUMENT AS M_INSTRUMENT,   PLIN.M_CURRENCY AS M_EN_CUR,   TO_DATE(@E_DATE:D,'YYYYMMDD') AS M_H_REP_DATE FROM TRN_ACJS_DBF ACJS LEFT OUTER JOIN TRN_ACA1_DBF A      ON ACJS.M_EN_ACCOUNT = A.M_REFERENCE LEFT OUTER JOIN TRN_ENTD_DBF EN      ON ACJS.M_ENTITY = EN.M_REF LEFT OUTER JOIN TRN_PLIN_DBF PLIN      ON ACJS.M_INSTRUMENT = PLIN.M_ID WHERE ACJS.M_EN_DATE=@E_DATE:D

SELECT   EXT.M_TRADE_REF,EXT.M_ORIG_TRADE,  EXT.M_EVT_INTID,  EXT.M_EVT_REF,  EXT.M_ACT_DATE,  UDF.M_COMMENTS1,  UDF.M_REASON FROM TRN_EXT_DBF EXT, TABLE#DATA#EVENT_DBF UDF /*MORE EVENTS TO BE ADDED TO THE LIST AS PER THE USER CONFIRMATION*/ WHERE EXT.M_EVT_INTID IN ('1.220','1.372') AND EXT.M_ACTION<>8 AND EXT.M_EVT_REF=UDF.M_REFERENCE AND EXT.M_ACT_DATE>=@ST_MNT_DT:D AND EXT.M_ACT_DATE<=@EN_MNT_DT:D

column21: SELECT   A.M_CTN, C.M_SCENARIO,   CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN A.M_TYPE LIKE '%HEDGED%' THEN C.M_RESULTV*A.PERCENTAGE ELSE 0.00 END) AS NUMERIC(12,2)) AS M_HEDGEDDIFF,   CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN A.M_TYPE LIKE '%HEDGING%' THEN C.M_RESULTV*A.PERCENTAGE  ELSE 0.00 END) AS NUMERIC(12,2)) AS M_HEDGINGDIF,   CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN A.M_TYPE LIKE '%THEORETICAL%' THEN C.M_RESULTV*A.PERCENTAGE  ELSE 0.00 END) AS NUMERIC(12,2))  AS M_THDIFF     FROM    (  SELECT   E.M_CTN,   F.M_TRADE_OREF,   'HEDGED' AS M_TYPE,  F.M_QUANTITY/F.M_INIT_QTY AS PERCENTAGE  FROM   HEDGE#HDGD_COMPL_DBF E, HEDGE#HDG_COMP_DBF F   WHERE   E.M_REF =F.M_REFERENCE      UNION ALL      SELECT   G.M_CTN,   H.M_TRADE_OREF,   'HEDGING' AS M_TYPE,  H.M_QUANTITY/H.M_INIT_QTY AS PERCENTAGE   FROM  HEDGE#HDGG_COMPL_DBF G, HEDGE#HDG_COMP_DBF H   WHERE   G.M_REF =H.M_REFERENCE      UNION ALL      SELECT   I.M_CTN,   J.M_TRADE_OREF,   'THEORETICAL' AS M_TYPE,  J.M_QUANTITY/J.M_INIT_QTY AS PERCENTAGE   FROM  HEDGE#THEO_COMPL_DBF I, HEDGE#HDG_COMP_DBF J   WHERE   I.M_REF = J.M_REFERENCE  )A, STD#VR_VR1 B, STD#VR_VR2 C     WHERE   B.M_DEALNUM IN (SELECT K.M_NB FROM TRN_HDR_DBF K WHERE K.M_TRN_STATUS <> 'DEAD' AND K.M_MRPL_ONB = A.M_TRADE_OREF)  AND B.M_KEY_ID = C.M_KEY_ID   AND C.M_OTYPE=2  GROUP BY A.M_CTN, C.M_SCENARIO  ORDER BY A.M_CTN, C.M_SCENARIO    /*SELECT  A.M_CTN, C.M_SCENARIO,  CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN A.M_TYPE LIKE '%HEDGED%' THEN C.M_RESULTV ELSE 0.00 END) AS NUMERIC(12,2)) AS M_HEDGEDDIFF,  CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN A.M_TYPE LIKE '%HEDGING%' THEN C.M_RESULTV ELSE 0.00 END) AS NUMERIC(12,2)) AS M_HEDGINGDIF,  CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN A.M_TYPE LIKE '%THEORETICAL%' THEN C.M_RESULTV ELSE 0.00 END) AS NUMERIC(12,2))  AS M_THDIFF  FROM   ( SELECT  E.M_CTN,  F.M_TRADE_OREF,  'HEDGED' AS M_TYPE  FROM  HEDGE#HDGD_COMPL_DBF E, HEDGE#HDG_COMP_DBF F  WHERE  E.M_REF =F.M_REFERENCE   UNION ALL   SELECT  G.M_CTN,  H.M_TRADE_OREF,  'HEDGING' AS M_TYPE  FROM HEDGE#HDGG_COMPL_DBF G, HEDGE#HDG_COMP_DBF H  WHERE  G.M_REF =H.M_REFERENCE   UNION ALL   SELECT  I.M_CTN,  J.M_TRADE_OREF,  'THEORETICAL' AS M_TYPE  FROM HEDGE#THEO_COMPL_DBF I, HEDGE#HDG_COMP_DBF J  WHERE  I.M_REF = J.M_REFERENCE )A, STD#VR_VR1 B, STD#VR_VR2 C  WHERE  A.M_TRADE_OREF = B.M_DEALNUM  AND B.M_KEY_ID = C.M_KEY_ID  AND C.M_OTYPE=2 GROUP BY A.M_CTN, C.M_SCENARIO ORDER BY A.M_CTN, C.M_SCENARIO*/
